headline: L3Harris Receives Multi-Year Javelin Solid Rocket Motor Contract
summary: MELBOURNE, Fla., September 15, 2025--L3Harris Technologies (NYSE: LHX) has received a contract valued up to $292 million to continue its role producing propulsion for the Javelin weapon system. The award is the largest propulsion production contract received to date for the Javelin program, representing a production extension for five years.
